The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Bradman exhibition

New Delhi: The Bradman exhibition, a unique display of memorabilia related to the greatest-ever batsman in cricket history, will travel to India, courtesy sponsorship by the Australian government. 

We will contribute $ 1m (Aus) in sponsorship towards the Bradman exhibition tour of India, visiting Australian Prime Ministe John Howard said here on Monday. 

The exhibition, scheduled for later this year, will tour New Delhi, Mumbai, Chennai and Calcutta. (Pti) 




